# Parlera Privacy Policy

Last updated: Jan. 15, 2022

Pertains to: the app "Parlera - word guessing game" by Enjoying FOSS

The app Parlera doesn't collect any personal information whatsoever. No analytics, no personal data, nothing ad-related. There isn't even a server side to the app.

All your data stays strictly on your device unless you deliberately and knowingly share it with someone using Parlera's Share functionality or similar â€” in which case it will be shared only with the people you specifically choose.